Sampled Waveforms And Musical Instruments - is a collection of free
software for editing and sharing MIDI instruments and sounds. Swami
aims to provide cross platform (Linux, Windows and Mac OSX) instrument
editing and sharing software for instrument formats such as SoundFont,
DLS and GigaSampler

Requires: libinstpatch, libgnomecanvas
Optional for playback: fluidsynth (in that case + lash + jack)
